While the number of new coronavirus cases is at a historic high, the Trump admin. is making another effort to get rid of Obamacare. Its top lawyer filed papers last night, urging the Supreme Court to strike down the Affordable Care Act.

@Weijia Jiang is at the White House. https://t.co/1nmz93LFdi
